== 最大贏家及獲益金額 ==
{{link-en|皮考尔|Jeffry Picower}}被认为是麦道夫投资丑闻中的最大受益者。根据麦道夫案资产清算托管人{{link-en|皮卡德|Irving Picard}}提交的法庭文件指出，从1970年代开始，皮考尔和他妻子芭芭拉（Barbara Picower）经营的一个基金会从麦道夫的投资中获取了72亿美元的收益。<ref>{{Cite web|title=麥道夫案最大受益者溺亡--跨國公司--人民網|url=http://mnc.people.com.cn/BIG5/10263954.html|work=mnc.people.com.cn|accessdate=2019-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505134740/http://mnc.people.com.cn/BIG5/10263954.html|archive-date=2019-05-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。皮考尔于2009年10月因心脏病发，于佛罗里达住宅游泳池溺斃，美国检方未对他提出任何指控<ref>{{Cite news|title=Investor With Madoff Is Found Dead in His Pool|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/26/business/26madoff.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2009-10-25|accessdate=2021-04-12|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Diana B.|last=Henriques|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412020847/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/26/business/26madoff.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Jeffry Picower, Madoff Money Man, Found Dead in His Pool|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/jeffry-picower-madoff-money-man-found-dead-in-his-pool/|accessdate=2021-04-12|work=www.cbsnews.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501144116/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/jeffry-picower-madoff-money-man-found-dead-in-his-pool/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其遗孀与皮卡德之后达成和解，同意交还72亿美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=馬多夫受害者 - 財經要聞|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20101219000005-260202?chdtv|work=中時電子報|accessdate=2019-05-05|language=zh-TW|last=中時電子報|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915012441/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20101219000005-260202?chdtv|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Heart Attack: Natural Causes Send Madoff Billionaire to the Bottom of the Pool|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/jeffry-picower-autospy-results-drowning-heart-attack/story?id=8917602|accessdate=2021-04-12|last=News|first=A. B. C.|work=ABC News|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412020847/https://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/jeffry-picower-autospy-results-drowning-heart-attack/story?id=8917602|dead-url=no}}</ref>

